<!-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê -->
<script>
    import { gsap } from "gsap";
    import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";

    gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

    const initHeroNames = () => {
        console.log("üíë Iniciando secci√≥n de nombres...");

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê ESTADO INICIAL ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        gsap.set("#contenedor-nombres", { opacity: 0, y: 50 });

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê ANIMACI√ìN PRINCIPAL ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        ScrollTrigger.create({
            trigger: "#contenedor-nombres",
            start: "top 75%",
            end: "top 20%",

            onEnter: () => {
                const tl = gsap.timeline();

                // Contenedor aparece
                tl.to("#contenedor-nombres", {
                    opacity: 1,
                    y: 0,
                    duration: 1.2,
                    ease: "power3.out",
                })

                    // P√°rrafos aparecen
                    .to(
                        "#parrafo-1",
                        {
                            opacity: 1,
                            y: 0,
                            duration: 1,
                            ease: "power2.out",
                        },
                        0.3,
                    )
                    .to(
                        "#parrafo-2",
                        {
                            opacity: 1,
                            y: 0,
                            duration: 1,
                            ease: "power2.out",
                        },
                        0.5,
                    )

                    // Nombres aparecen
                    .to(
                        "#nombre-1",
                        {
                            opacity: 1,
                            y: 0,
                            duration: 1.2,
                            ease: "power2.out",
                        },
                        0.9,
                    )
                    .to(
                        "#ampersand",
                        {
                            opacity: 1,
                            scale: 1,
                            duration: 0.8,
                            ease: "back.out(1.4)",
                        },
                        1.2,
                    )
                    .to(
                        "#nombre-2",
                        {
                            opacity: 1,
                            y: 0,
                            duration: 1.2,
                            ease: "power2.out",
                        },
                        1.4,
                    );
            },

            onLeaveBack: () => {
                const tl = gsap.timeline();
                tl.to(
                    "#nombre-2, #ampersand, #nombre-1, #parrafo-2, #parrafo-1",
                    {
                        opacity: 0,
                        duration: 0.3,
                        stagger: 0.05,
                    },
                ).to(
                    "#contenedor-nombres",
                    {
                        opacity: 0,
                        y: 50,
                        duration: 0.5,
                    },
                    "<",
                );
            },
        });

        console.log("üíë‚ú® Secci√≥n de nombres activada!");
    };

    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", initHeroNames);
    document.addEventListener("astro:page-load", initHeroNames);
</script>
